    <item>
      <title>先锋首席经济学家：特朗普“不确定性税”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-06/vanguard-chief-economist-trump-an-uncertainty-tax</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金融市场表明，随着与关联相关的不确定性和经济弱点的指标，衰退的风险正在越来越多。 在市场上狂奔之后，经济经理和企业高管努力应对总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的威胁关税所创造的波动性，经济情绪正在变黑。特朗普捍卫了他在周二晚上致国会的讲话中重制全球交易秩序的计划，承认未来的不适感。 Vanguard，Joe Davis的全球首席经济学家和全球投资战略负责人在彭博广播电台与Stephen Carroll和Valerie Tytel进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-06/vanguard-chief-economist-trump-an-uncertainty-tax</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 14:17:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国失业者索赔返回静态水平，为221,000</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-06/us-jobless-claims-return-to-muted-levels-at-221-000-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周，美国失业申请减少了21,000至221,000，而持续的索赔则增加到190万。迈克尔·麦基（Michael McKee）分解了彭博电视台（Bloomberg Television）上的数字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-06/us-jobless-claims-return-to-muted-levels-at-221-000-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 13:53:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国失业索赔下降，对劳动力市场的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/us-jobless-claims-drop-to-221-000-returning-to-muted-levels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周为美国失业福利的申请下降，并在年初恢复到静态的水平，此前有报道称劳动力市场状况恶化后，提供了一些救济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/us-jobless-claims-drop-to-221-000-returning-to-muted-levels</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 13:33:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国贸易赤字在特朗普关税之前飙升至记录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/us-trade-deficit-surges-to-a-record-ahead-of-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当公司争先恐后地从海外获得货物，唐纳德·特朗普总统对美国最大的贸易伙伴征收关税，美国的贸易赤字在一月份扩大到了记录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/us-trade-deficit-surges-to-a-record-ahead-of-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 13:31:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税前运行驱动器记录加拿大 - 美国贸易盈余</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/tariff-front-running-drives-record-high-canada-us-trade-surplus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大对美国的出口在一月份因汽车，汽车零件和能源的运输而激增，促使北国与美国发布了创纪录的贸易盈余。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/tariff-front-running-drives-record-high-canada-us-trade-surplus</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 13:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行再次削减，信号放松阶段即将结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/ecb-cuts-again-and-signals-easing-phase-is-nearing-its-end</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲中央银行自6月以来的第六次降低了利率，并表示随着通货膨胀的降温和经济的消化，地缘政治的地震变化可能会接近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/ecb-cuts-again-and-signals-easing-phase-is-nearing-its-end</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 13:18:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅尔罗斯首席执行官：关税不是威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-06/melrose-industries-ceo-peter-dilnot-tariffs-not-a-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[公民和国防航空公司公司首席执行官彼得·迪尔诺特（Peter Dilnot）表示，预计关税不会颠覆梅尔罗斯的订单书。取而代之的是，他预计全球航空航天行业以及梅尔罗斯（Melrose）的售后业务的增长会更高。彼得在“彭博社：开业交易”上与安娜·爱德华兹，盖伊·约翰逊和汤姆·麦肯齐进行了交谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-06/melrose-industries-ceo-peter-dilnot-tariffs-not-a-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 10:15:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自1990年以来，德国债券溃败最糟糕的是促使世界各地抛售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/japan-s-10-year-bond-yield-reaches-highest-since-june-2009</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国的债券扩大了溃败，随着柏林历史性计划释放数千亿欧元的国防和基础设施的历史性计划，全球债务市场滑行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/japan-s-10-year-bond-yield-reaches-highest-since-june-2009</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 00:27:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>急剧下降后的石油稳定将价格推向超卖区</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易者继续消化特朗普总统对美国主要贸易伙伴的广泛关税和欧佩克+意外的生产猛增，因此在几乎不动的价格下降后，石油越来越高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 23:29:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
